➜“加，减，乘，除”的英语都不会？英语和数学老师在盯着你
http://www.sohu.com/a/433640570_115013	3217
<p>Today we're going to talk about some basic math vocabulary. This vocabulary is very simple but can come in handy if you're going to study abroad or if you just want to learn more English.</p>
<p>今天我们将讨论一些基本的数学词汇。这个词汇非常简单，但是如果你要出国留学或者你想学更多的英语，它可以派上大用场。</p>
<p>The first set of words were going to talk about are operations.</p>
<p>我们要讲的第一组词是operations运算。</p>
<p>The most common operations are addition, subtraction,</p>
<p>multiplication and division, and those are what we'll talk about today.</p>
<p>最常见的运算是加、减、乘、除，这些就是我们今天要讨论的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201123/199ba936eed94b44b877948ed19f0e29.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Addition is when you add two numbers together. This is called a plus sign. So for example, 4 plus 5 equals 9 or if I have 4 and add 5 I get 9.</p>
<p>加法就是两个数相加。这叫做加号。例如，4 + 5 = 9，或者说我有4，再加5，得到9。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201123/f3da5efa1ff649b6afae99bc27fee56c.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
