</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>Subtraction is when you subtract one number from another number. This is called a minus sign. So for example 6 minus 4 equals 2 or if I have 6 and take away 4 I get 2.</p>
<p>减法就是用一个数减去另一个数。这叫做减号。例如，6 - 4 = 2，如果我有6，拿走4，得到2。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201123/0fbc15e5172c4a77897afd9bfa599f77.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Multiplication is when you multiply one number by another number. For example 4 times 3 equals 12 or</p>
<p>if I multiply 4 by 3 I get 12.</p>
<p>乘法就是用一个数乘以另一个数。例如，4乘以3等于12，或者4乘以3得到12。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201123/09d167ed7d11466ea7e27aa85bbfb0a0.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Division is when you divide one number by another</p>
<p>number. For example 12 divided by 2 equals 6 or if I divide 12 by 2 I get 6.</p>
<p>除法就是用一个数除以另一个数。例如，12除以2等于6，或者12除以2得到6。</p>
<p>Hopefully this has helped you it's very basic English but teachers don't talk about this vocabulary very often. Thank you for watching.</p>
<p>希望这对你有帮助，这是非常基础的英语，但是老师不会经常谈论这个词汇，谢谢。</p>
<p>今天的内容都学会了么?</p>
